Uses of Package
de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.core

Packages that use de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.core
de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.core Contains core classes to parse service definitions (OWL-S) and referenced datatypes, that are descriped in ontologies (OWL). 
de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.grounding Contains a builder class for building WSDL definitions and OWL-S definitions incl WSDL Grounding in the context of re-engineering process. 
de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.gui Contains GUI classes (OWLS2WSDL translation tool) 
de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.gui.models Contains all models needed by the GUI (OWLS2WSDL translation tool) 
de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.parser Contains main parser class and a container class for collected data that is based on the JENA specific object model
